description:
On today’s show, Emily’s discussing snooping – because lots of us do it and it’s not serving us. Plus, she’s taking your calls.

She talks about the good old google search/social media stalk many of us are guilty of doing, what to do when you were having great sex – then you went on vacation and your partner’s not into it, backdoor play – your partner’s ready, but you’re not sure, you’re married, you like giving head to other men, but your wife is unsure about it – what’s next?
